{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC05_KEI_660.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x16,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x13,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "However, you should understand by now that a person's ego always leads down this direction, after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "And your sister was most likely seized by the malice of ancient times, like this one."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "The malice of ancient times...? But if that's the case, what should I do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Is it necessary to shirk away from malice? Just challenge it head-on, like me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "I see. But still..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Is it...really malice?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "The being that captured Nio, did it do it out of malice?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Maybe there was some other reason it did it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x130,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Now this is surprising. Are you going to defend the being that captured your sister?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x133,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "To capture a living human, absorb it, and eliminate its presence from the world..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x135,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "If that's not malice, then what is it supposed to be?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "...I don't know. But I can't believe that its reason is to eliminate them."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Because Nio is still alive, and is still able to smile."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x136,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... That's a very curious assumption, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x14,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Now is not the time to think about such things. You should be more active."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "That's...true. I'm sorry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x196,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "No... The being that I concluded to be driven by malice... You say it's possible that it's not..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I don't know which one of us is correct. However..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Seeing it with our own eyes may give us the answer."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0xe7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "There might be something that can lead us to your sister further down. Let's split up and search."
        }
    ]
}